_sText:
1v1_metro is a port of the 1v1_metro map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

1v1 Metro is a small map made for 1v1's and some custom game modes. 

It takes place in a (you guessed it) metro station. 

Metro features alternate passages to catch your opponent off guard and height changes to mix things up. 

Look forwards to ruining friendships, and have fun!
